data.text:
Joseph Evan, Ph.D., ’95, provost and vice president for academic affairs at King’s College, today acknowledged the more than 600 students who qualified for the Spring 2024 Dean’s List.

Full-time undergraduate students qualify when they earn a 3.5 GPA or higher in the given semester. Students’ names and hometowns are listed below alphabetically.
